### ========== 1. 用户认证模块 ==========

### 1.1 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 1.2 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ========== 2. 防诈骗案例模块 ==========

### 2.1 创建案例
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "网络刷单诈骗案例",
  "content": "某用户在网上看到刷单广告，承诺高额返利，结果被骗5000元",
  "category": "网络诈骗",
  "fraudType": "刷单诈骗",
  "victimInfo": "受害者为大学生，损失金额5000元",
  "warningTips": "不要相信任何刷单兼职，都是诈骗",
  "authorId": 1
}

### 2.2 获取所有案例
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cases

### 2.3 获取单个案例
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cases/7

### 2.4 按分类获取案例（使用URL编码）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cases/category/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97

### 2.5 点赞案例
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cases/7/like

### ========== 3. 社区帖子模块 ==========

### 3.1 创建帖子
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "如何识别网络诈骗",
  "content": "分享一些识别网络诈骗的技巧和经验",
  "authorId": 1
}

### 3.2 获取所有帖子
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts

### 3.3 获取单个帖子
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1

### 3.4 获取用户帖子
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/author/1

### 3.5 点赞帖子
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1/like

### ========== 4. 评论模块 ==========

### 4.1 创建评论
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "authorId": 1,
  "content": "非常有用的分享，谢谢！",
  "parentId": null
}

### 4.2 创建回复评论
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "authorId": 1,
  "content": "同意楼上观点",
  "parentId": 1
}

### 4.3 获取帖子评论
GET http://localhost:8080/api/comments/post/1

### 4.4 点赞评论
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments/1/like

### ========== 5. 防诈骗知识模块 ==========

### 5.1 创建知识
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "如何防范电信诈骗",
  "content": "电信诈骗的常见手法和防范措施，包括冒充公检法、中奖诈骗等",
  "category": "防诈骗知识",
  "tags": "电信诈骗,防范措施",
  "authorId": 1
}

### 5.2 获取所有知识
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge

### 5.3 获取单个知识
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/3

### 5.4 按分类获取知识（使用URL编码）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/category/%E9%98%B2%E8%AF%88%E8%AF%88%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86

### 5.5 按标签获取知识（使用URL编码）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/tag/%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97

### 5.6 点赞知识
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/3/like

### ========== 6. 举报模块 ==========

### 6.1 创建举报
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reporterId": 1,
  "reportedType": "post",
  "reportedId": 1,
  "reason": "违规内容",
  "description": "该帖子包含不当言论"
}

### 6.2 获取所有举报
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reports

### 6.3 获取单个举报
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reports/3

### 6.4 获取用户举报
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reports/reporter/1

### 6.5 按状态获取举报
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reports/status/pending

### 6.6 更新举报状态
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reports/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "processed"
}

### ========== 清理测试数据 ==========

### 删除评论
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/comments/1

### 删除帖子
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1

### 删除知识
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/1

### 删除案例
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/cases/1

### 删除举报
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/reports/1